<br>
That's the whole problem : there is NO way to provide -any- evidence either way with those machines. There is no paper trail. There are no more exit polls. So... in all seriousness, how professional is it to introduce a system that has zero validation control for such critical task ? Doesn't it look a little suspiscious at least ?<br>
<br>
<br>
